pageContext.claim: “Always heard that as President, ‘it’s all about the economy!’ Well, we have one of the best economies in the history of our Country. Big GDP, lowest unemployment, companies coming back to the U.S. in BIG numbers, great new trade deals happening, & more. But LITTLE media mention!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump exaggerates his record on jobs and the economy. He inherited a growing economy from President Obama and the rate of growth has not appreciably accelerated during Trump's two years in office.
